# 🎯 Bubble Game

A fast-paced number-matching game built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript! Click the bubbles that match the target number before the timer runs out.

## 🔹 How to Play
- A random number appears at the top.
- Click all bubbles with the same number to score points.
- The game ends when the timer hits zero—try to beat your high score!

## 🎮 Live Demo
[Play now](https://aman3520.github.io/Bubble-Game/)

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- HTML5
- CSS3 (fully responsive)
- Vanilla JavaScript

## 📱 Responsive
Fully playable on desktop, tablet, and mobile!

